data.name: Business Term Deposit 2 mths
data.description: Fixed Term Deposits start from as little as $2,000, and you can choose terms that works for your Business/Trust/SMSF between 30 days and 24 months

features.additionalInfo: View your term deposit with convenient Online Banking.
Fixed rate for the life of the Term.

constraints.additionalInfo: Business term deposits are exclusive to: Sole Traders, Corporates (including Corporate Trustees), Individual Trustees, SMSF, Partnerships, Incorporated Associations (not-for-profits organisations and clubs).

fees.name: Early Withdrawal Penalty
fees.additionalInfo: Early withdrawal may incurr a partial loss of interest accrued depending on the Term remaining at the time of ealry withdrawal.

depositRates.additionalInfo: Where terms exceed 12 months, interest is capitalised annually. Interest payable in respect of the last 12 months or part thereof is added to the balance at maturity.
